{
  "texts": [
    "The ASAP dataset (Hamner et al. 2012) is a popular dataset in AES tasks.",
    "It is a free and publicly available dataset published on Kaggle for Automated Student Assessment Prize (ASAP) competition 2 in 2012.",
    "It contains 8 prompts and more than 12,900 essays written by students from grade 7 up to 10.",
    "The prompts represent different topics and genres of essays, namely argumentative, response and narrative.",
    "Prompt 1 and 2 require opinions of students that can be defined as argumentative essay."
  ]
}